OL,3,CChildren's hospice fears for its
OL,4,Cfuture over National Insurance hike
OL,6,FHowever, costs are rising and this
OL,7,Fyear there is a #1 million shortfall -
OL,8,Feven before the rise in employers'
OL,9,FNational Insurance.
OL,11,FThe changes mean the charity is going
OL,12,Fto have to find an extra #242,000 and
OL,13,Fthat is likely to have an impact on
OL,14,Fservices.
