OL,3,CChildren's hospice fears for its
OL,4,Cfuture over National Insurance hike
OL,6,FMike Bartlett, Julia's House, said:
OL,7,F"It could mean waiting lists, it could
OL,8,Fmean shaping the service in a
OL,9,Fdifferent way, this is a big extra
OL,10,Fcost that we were not expecting, we
OL,11,Fare going to have to look very hard at
OL,12,Fthe services we can provide going
OL,13,Fforwards."
OL,15,FSeventy carers and nurses work for the
OL,16,Fcharity and the increase in employers'
OL,17,FNational Insurance is the equivalent
OL,18,Fcost of six highly qualified nurses.
OL,20,FBut compromising care is not an option
OL,21,Ffor the charity.
