OL,3,CChildren's hospice fears for its
OL,4,Cfuture over National Insurance hike
OL,6,FLydia Absolon, Senior Nurse, Julia's
OL,7,FHouse, said: "We pride ourselves on
OL,8,Fthe care we give here, it's to a high
OL,9,Fstandard and to be able to do that we
OL,10,Fneed one to one care.
OL,12,F"These children are complex, even
OL,13,Ftheir communication is complex, we
OL,14,Fneed staff to be with them at all
OL,15,Ftimes."
