OL,4,Cfuture over National Insurance hike
OL,6,FThere was a campaign meeting today in
OL,7,FParliament where the Chief Executive
OL,8,Fof Julia's House and local MPs lobbied
OL,9,Ffor an exemption from the tax
OL,10,Fincrease. However there was no
OL,11,Fprogress.
