OL,3,CChildren's hospice fears for its
OL,4,Cfuture over National Insurance hike
OL,6,FMartin Edwards, CEO of Julia's House,
OL,7,Fsaid: "The Treasury have said no
OL,8,Fyou're not going to get an exemption
OL,9,Fso what is the Department of Health
OL,10,Fgoing to do about this in order to
OL,11,Fmake sure these patients can continue
OL,12,Fto be treated where they want to be,
OL,13,Fin the children's hospice or adult
OL,14,Fhospice that they know, who know them.
OL,15,FThis is the best care that they can
OL,16,Fget. They don't need to go back into
OL,17,Fhospital."
